_sText:
This is the second and hopefully final version of this map.

Change/update log
-Reduced grass by half to reduce lag on low-end machines
-Removed the swaying of the grass to reduce lag on low-end machines
-Added more trash/junk models around the map(like in cod4)
-Added a mound at CT spawn (like in cod4)
-Changed some of the crates to be opened (like in cod4)
-Added another crane to the dock(like in cod4)
-Included a NAV file with the download

This map is a remake of COD4s map shipment. It is meant to be a similar port, that can be used for different gametypes like gungame, DM, or normal play (kill the other team)

I also added a GunGame4 spawnpoint file for deathmatch servers. You would place es_fy_shipment_v2.sqldb in addons/eventscripts/gungame4/addons/gg_deathmatch/spawnpoints
